name: SquareShells
body:
### Welcome SquareShells.
SquareShells was founded by @barksten in 2014. 

SquareShells are focused on (but not limited to) iOS and Mac software. We're always interested in collaboration projects!

### Support or Contact
Having some trouble with this or just some questions? Email contact@squareshells.com and you'll be heard. If you prefer a shorter message you can tweet to [@squareshells](http://twitter.com/squareshells).
